Package: family
Title: A Simpler Way to Find Related Directories
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Mauro",
           family = "Lepore",
           role = c("aut", "ctr", "cre"),
           email = "maurolepore@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1986-7988"))
Description: Find a family of related directories without
    knowing their name.  Find children directories under a parent
    directory, the siblings of any one child, and the parent of all
    children.  Inspired by the work by Jim Hester (<
    https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=here>).  directories.
